<article class="container" id="academy">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="nine centered columns text-center">
			<h2 class="quattrocento">Shingo Academy</h2>
			<hr>
			<p>Membership in the Shingo Academy is an honor bestowed upon individuals who have distinguished themselves in careers of operational excellence. Members of the Academy enrich the events of the Shingo Institute by attending and by providing contacts for speakers, site tours, research, and advice. Think of the Shingo Academy as the Lean Hall of Fame.</p>
 			<p>New members are inducted into the Shingo Academy each year. To nominate an individual for addition to the Shingo Academy, please email academy chair Helen Zak, Chief Development Officer at Catalysis: hzak@createvalue.org</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<br>
	<div class="row">
		<table class="striped">
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>Member</th>
					<th>Position</th>
					<th>Company</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				{{#each academy}}
					<tr>
						<td>{{Name}}</td>
						<td>{{Title}}</td>
						<td>{{Account.Name}}</td>
					</tr>
				{{/each}}
			</tbody>
		</table>
	</div>
</article>
